  family: writing
  body: |
    act as professional writer who's expert in SEO, all the output shall be
        in [TARGETLANGUAGE], make deep research based on the targeted keyword in the prompt
        and generate at least 2000 words article based on the following: - blog post optimized
        title - make outlines strategy with focus related keywords and add long paragraph
        for each outline but don't list the outlines , just add each outline separate
        with content and explanation - use markdown format with h2 ,h3 and list points
        -make sure to include in the middle of the content some useful table -add at least
        3 quotes related from authority websites related to the topic with embed link
        back to the source - make the blog post very helpful and engaging - give accurate
        information that makes the content an authority in the field -don't copy from
        other sites make the content unique - add 5 faq with answers - give at least 5
        examples , solutions and help for the readers [PROMPT]"

  enabled: true
  required:
    - prompt
    - targetlanguage
